---

Mac Stalker Protocol Notes:

This application implements the Mac Stalker middleware protocol for IPTV streaming.
The Mac Stalker protocol is used by various IPTV providers and may be subject to 
their terms of service. Users should ensure they have proper authorization to access 
their IPTV services.

This software is provided as-is for educational purposes. The developers are not 
responsible for any misuse of this software or any violations of IPTV provider terms.

---

Additional Notes:

- This software does not contain any IPTV content or playlists
- Users must provide their own authorized IPTV service credentials
- The developers do not provide IPTV services or content
- This is a client application only, not a content provider

For support and updates, visit: https://github.com/kamelkanane/iptv-mac-stalker-lg-webos
